name: ChoDoo-soonBurnInHell
description:
Cho Doo-soon is still enjoying his life of sins, I know you are angry,so are parents of many, but we want to take actions, since the justice system didn't give the justice. Just in case you don't know what we are talking about, please google it.
After so much suffering he caused to the 8 year old girl,Cho was released and protected. If he doesn't rot in jail, he has to burn in hell. We will try our best.
The reserved 7% will be given to thoes who helped excute the missiong.
The fund will be used to get the job done, the rest will be used to hunt other monsters like Cho,based on the voting of the community
payDisclosure: This is not a financial investment, do your research before your contribution
